 After the patch:\\n- `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=com.tunnelvisionlabs:antlr4-annotations:4.5 --stacktrace` passed\\n- `./gradlew runNativeTraceImage -Pcoordinates=com.tunnelvisionlabs:antlr4-annotations:4.5 ...` finished with binary exit `0`\\n- `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.tunnelvisionlabs:antlr4-annotations:4.5 --stacktrace` passed\\n\\n`generateMetadata` was not usable with this GraalVM because `native-image-agent` is not loadable in this environment, so the fix was done from the exact-metadata trace failure instead.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"turn.completed\",\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3266692,\"cached_input_tokens\":3155456,\"output_tokens\":15126,\"reasoning_output_tokens\":4954}}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
